---
// How It Works - 3 steps
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/30">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
      Up and running in 3 steps
    </h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      No complex setup. No lengthy onboarding. Deploy and start handling guests in minutes.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">
            1
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Deploy</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
              One click on Railway or Docker. Your own server, your own data. Under 5 minutes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">
            2
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Connect</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
              Link your WhatsApp, SMS, or email. Add your hotel's knowledge and policies.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">
            3
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Relax</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
              Jack handles guest inquiries automatically. Get notified only when you're needed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
